# Determinate

⚠️ **Deprecation warning** ⚠️

This component has been deprecated and is no longer maintained. We recommend using the `loader` component instead.

## Installation & Import

```bash
yarn add @ids-ts/determinate
```

```tsx
import { Determinate, DeterminateLong, DeterminateShort } from '@ids-ts/determinate';
```

## Sub-Components

### DeterminateLong

| Prop | Type | Required | Description |
| --- | --- | --- | --- |
| `automationId` | `string` | No | This prop is used for testing purposes |
| `checkRounded` | `boolean` | No | If determinate and ending with checkmark, true if checkmark should be rounded. |
| `checkStrokeWidth` | `number` | No | If determinate and ending with checkmark, stroke width for checkmark. |
| `endWithCheckmark` | `boolean` | No | End with a checkmark. Only for determinate types. |
| `endWithFill` | `boolean` | No | End by filling the spinner circle. Only for determinate types. |
| `progress` | `number` | No | Current percentage of the progress bar that is filled. |
| `size` | `number` | Yes | Height and width of the spinner: 24 - 64 (px). |

